latestIgtvVideos.title: WILL YOU STILL MARRY ME? 💕
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It's been a year since you asked me to marry you, so much has happened since. 
We planned our wedding tirelessly, only for it to get postponed, this broke my heart. From being exhausted travelling and being home less than a week a month, we were suddenly locked down for 6, this was amazing. It was like being stranded on an island with my favorite person. It's been a year of ups and downs, straight roads and steep slopes, but everytime I asked myself, in the good times and bad, do I still want to marry you? The answer was always YES! Which is why this time I ask, WILL YOU STILL MARRY ME? Because I'd like to be your wife every single life. Like I said last year, one lifetime with you is not enough! @neilsanghvi_

It took me some time to decide whether to share this moment or not, but then I thought of all my fellow brides to be, it's been a tough year for us all, this one's for all of you! Knowing that we have the love of our lives by our side, makes things a whole lot easier. Wedding dates and celebrations are short lived, here’s to building a marriage with your loved one and knowing we survived the craziest of times!

#NeilDownForSonam or should I say #SonamNeilDown

Music and Voice by the beautiful @devangichopra - can't thank you enough! 

#Fashioneiress
